  <h2>The Bottom Line</h2>
  <p>Selling as-is to a cash buyer is the right move for a specific type of seller: someone who values speed, certainty, and simplicity over maximizing sale price. If that's you, it's a really good option. If it's not — we'll tell you that too.</p>

